    mj-text(padding="0" mj-class="T20-700 cR") So how do you get started ?
    mj-text(padding="0" mj-class="T15-400") The main applicant must be at least 18 years of age.
    mj-text(padding="0" mj-class="T15-400") Applicants must show proof of capital of no less than EUR 500,000 (EUR 150,000 of which should be in financial assets).
    mj-text(padding="0" mj-class="T15-400") A property purchase of EUR 350,000 (EUR 300,000 in South Malta or Gozo) or a property lease of EUR 12,000 per annum (EUR 10,000 in South Malta or Gozo).
    mj-text(padding="0" mj-class="T15-400") You must be a third-country national (i.e. not from an EU or EEA state).
    mj-text(padding="0" mj-class="T15-400") Evidence of a clean criminal record.
